# ============================================
# Logs
# ============================================
logs/
# But never ignore application source that lives in a directory named `logs`:
# the Next.js `app/api/logs` route and the NestJS `src/logs` read-API module.
!apps/web/app/api/logs/
!apps/web/app/api/logs/**
!apps/api/src/logs/
!apps/api/src/logs/**
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

